; Native-resolution courthouse walk: 24 frames span 286 source frames.
; preludes: form/form-stdlib/core.fk form/form-stdlib/form-fs.fk form/form-stdlib/str-byte-at.fk form/form-stdlib/file-byte-window.fk form/form-stdlib/crc32.fk form/form-stdlib/transformer-numerics.fk cognition/transformer-block.fk model/geometric-camera.fk model/lingbot-pytorch-checkpoint.fk model/lingbot-vision-input.fk model/lingbot-gca-runtime.fk model/lingbot-geometry-heads.fk form/form-stdlib/speaker-embed.fk form/form-stdlib/champion-challenger.fk form/form-stdlib/identity-match.fk form/form-stdlib/face-embed.fk form/form-stdlib/spatial-fusion.fk form/form-stdlib/world-model.fk form/form-stdlib/world-model-lingbot-map.fk model/lingbot-map-runtime.fk model/lingbot-real-life.fk observe/lingbot-map-real-life-acceptance.fk
